.TH MH-COMPRESSOR-MANAGER 1 "April 2026" "mh-compressor-manager 1.0.431" "General Commands Manual"
.SH NAME
mh-compressor-manager \- automatic static content compression for nginx
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B mh-compressor-manager
[\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBmh-compressor-manager\fP is a background service (daemon) for automatic compression of static web content for the nginx web server. The program monitors file system changes in real time and creates compressed copies of files in Gzip (.gz) and Brotli (.br) formats.
.PP
It uses \fBinotify\fP for real-time file system monitoring and a thread pool for parallel compression. Compressed files inherit metadata from the originals: permissions, owner/group, SELinux context, and modification time.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-\-config " \fIPATH\fR"
Path to configuration file (default: \fI/etc/mediahive/compressor-manager.conf\fR)
.TP
.BR \-\-dir " \fIPATH\fR"
Target directory (overrides \fBtarget_path\fR from config)
.TP
.BR \-\-ext " \fILIST\fR"
List of file extensions for compression (overrides \fBlist\fR from config, space-separated)
.TP
.BR \-\-gzip\-level " \fIN\fR"
Gzip compression level (1\-9, default: 9)
.TP
.BR \-\-brotli\-level " \fIN\fR"
Brotli compression level (1\-11, default: 11)
.TP
.BR \-\-min\-size " \fIN\fR"
Minimum file size for compression in bytes (default: 256, minimum: 256)
.TP
.BR \-\-min\-compress\-size " \fIN\fR"
Alias for \fB\-\-min\-size\fR
.TP
.B \-\-dry\-run
Dry run mode (show plans without actual compression)
.TP
.B \-\-debug
Debug logging mode (overrides \fBdebug\fR from config)
.TP
.BR \-\-process\-without\-ext
Process files without extensions
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Show help and exit
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-version
Show version and exit
.SH FILES
.TP
.I /etc/mediahive/compressor-manager.conf
Production configuration file (minimal, no comments)
.TP
.I /etc/mediahive/compressor-manager.conf.full
Full reference configuration (all parameters with documentation)
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Run with default settings:
.RS
.nf
mh-compressor-manager
.fi
.RE
.TP
Run with custom target directory:
.RS
.nf
mh-compressor-manager --dir /var/www/mysite
.fi
.RE
.TP
Dry run (no actual compression):
.RS
.nf
mh-compressor-manager --dry-run
.fi
.RE
.TP
Maximum compression:
.RS
.nf
mh-compressor-manager --gzip-level 9 --brotli-level 11
.fi
.RE
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.BR gzip (1),
.BR brotli (1),
.BR nginx (8),
.BR inotify (7),
.BR systemd.service (5)
